<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Review Received - Mang Crinkle</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* Review Details Styling */
    .review-summary {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .review-summary-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .review-detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
    }
    
    .review-detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .review-detail-label {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .review-detail-value {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .star-rating {
      color: #f59e0b;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .review-content {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      color: #374151;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    
    /* Order Details */
    .order-details {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .order-details-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .order-detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
    }
    
    .order-detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .order-detail-label {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .order-detail-value {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    /* Admin Button - matching admin-btn-primary with correct hover */
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f54900;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #ca3500;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">Mang Crinkle</div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">New Review Received</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">A customer has left a review for order #<%= @review.order.id %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello <%= @admin_user.display_name %>,</p>
          
          <p>A new customer review has been submitted and is now live on the website. Here are the details:</p>
          
          <div class="review-summary">
            <div class="review-summary-title">Review Details</div>
            
            <div class="review-detail-row">
              <span class="review-detail-label">Customer:</span>
              <span class="review-detail-value"><%= @review.customer_name %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="review-detail-row">
              <span class="review-detail-label">Rating:</span>
              <span class="review-detail-value">
                <span class="star-rating">
                  <% @review.rating.times do %>★<% end %>
                  <% (5 - @review.rating).times do %>☆<% end %>
                </span>
                (<%= @review.rating %>/5)
              </span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="review-detail-row">
              <span class="review-detail-label">Email:</span>
              <span class="review-detail-value"><%= @review.email %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="review-detail-row">
              <span class="review-detail-label">Submitted:</span>
              <span class="review-detail-value"><%= @review.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <% if @review.comment.present? %>
            <div class="content-section">
              <h3 style="color: #7e2a0c; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Customer Comment:</h3>
              <div class="review-content"><%= @review.comment %></div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          
          <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-details-title">Related Order Information</div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Order ID:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value">#<%= @review.order.id %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Order Date:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value"><%= @review.order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Order Total:</span>
              <span class="order-detail-value">$<%= sprintf('%.2f', @review.order.total_price) %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-detail-row">
              <span class="order-detail-label">Items Count:</span>
              <span class="review-detail-value"><%= @review.order.line_items.count %> item<%= @review.order.line_items.count == 1 ? '' : 's' %></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <p>The review is now live on the website and visible to customers. <% if @review.rating >= 4 %>This is a positive review that will help showcase our quality to potential customers!<% elsif @review.rating == 3 %>This review provides valuable feedback for improvement.<% else %>This review may require follow-up to address any concerns raised.<% end %></p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.admin_reviews_url(host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">View All Reviews</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>Review submitted on: <%= @review.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
          <p>Admin notification sent to: <%= @admin_user.email %></p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>Mang Crinkle Admin System</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 